data.description: This classic 1964 Rambling Ranch has plenty of room to roam.  Classic to this era, you will find some of the original hardwood floors and ceramic tile. Updating has been done throughout the house.  Over-sized Bonus room used as a entertaining area to invite your family and friends with tons of seating and gathering areas.  Additional large sun-room provides more entertaining areas and great views of nature.  Private office area, work out area and laundry room.    Bonus room could easily be converted to a 4th bedroom.   Come have fun with all this great space and customize it for all of your family's' needs.  Located on a on a quiet street , yet close to everything.
